title: Racoon Baby
description: Heard the crows howling the other day and came outside to see this poor little Racoon baby huddled halfway up the tree. They are enemies since racoons love crow eggs I hear. He finally crawled up to the top where he tried to shove his body in a squirrel nest for a few hours, tail hanging out. Not sure when the poor thing got down. He was in the party the night before with 4 other youngsters on our porch after we accidently leaving the cat food out. Youngsters.
creator: geckoam
